name: WSJ
text: Airlines are shipping more live animals, helping cover the drop in passenger flights. They must make sure giraffes don’t “bump their heads,” and give pigs “a little bit of encouragement.” https://t.co/ZEI2fAtvbt

text: Breaking: The number of patients hospitalized with Covid-19 hit a record, passing levels not seen since April. Scientists believe it will likely get worse. https://t.co/XVr7tR8VG7
